---
---
<section id="story" style="padding:7rem 4rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;background:var(--espresso)">
  <div class="reveal-left" style="aspect-ratio:4/5;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#3d2010,#2d1b0e);border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;position:relative">
    <div style="position:absolute;bottom:2rem;left:2rem;right:2rem">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:2rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.15);line-height:1.2">"Coffee is a language in itself."</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="reveal-right">
    <p style="font-size:.68rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--caramel);margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem"><span style="display:block;width:2rem;height:1px;background:var(--caramel)"></span>Our Story</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1.5rem;color:var(--warm)">A corner shop with a<br />big <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--caramel)">heart</em></h2>
    <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(250,248,244,.55);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1.2rem">Started in 2017 with a second-hand espresso machine, a lease on this corner shop, and an unwavering belief that great coffee doesn't need to be complicated — just careful.</p>
    <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:rgba(250,248,244,.55);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:2rem">We source directly from small farms in Ethiopia, Guatemala, and Colombia — visiting our partners annually to ensure fair pricing and sustainable practices.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:2.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--caramel);line-height:1">12+</div><div style="font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(250,248,244,.4);margin-top:.3rem">Farm partners</div></div>
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--caramel);line-height:1">40k+</div><div style="font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(250,248,244,.4);margin-top:.3rem">Cups served</div></div>
      <div><div style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--caramel);line-height:1">3</div><div style="font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(250,248,244,.4);margin-top:.3rem">Locations</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>@media(max-width:768px){section{grid-template-columns:1fr!important;padding:4rem 1.2rem!important}}</style>
